Scripts to create and mantain the internal RPM repo for RALPH.

Usage:

# Copy initial specs files to rpmbuild dir
$ cp *.in ~/rpmbuild/SPECS

# Build dependent package
$ rpmbuild -ba ~/rpmbuild/SPECS/InsightToolkit

# Copy deps to the public repository
$ ./copy_deps

# Build rpms
$ ./package_core
$ ./package_filters

# Rsync the public repo and update it
$ ./update_repo